author: Jason Silverstein
title: These 10 states still don't have stay-at-home coronavirus orders
description: About 90% of Americans are living under stay-at-home orders — but some governors are still resisting.
content:
It may seem like the entire United States is shutting down and staying indoors due to the coronavirus pandemic. But some parts of the country are still holding off.
